{"tid":1185265,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"歐盟就天安門廣場事件30週件發表聲明","createTime":"2019-06-04T07:16:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-04T07:21:19.000Z","uid":141151,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ed4332c480218162dbdb9ba2edf12be4c20a005a","tid":1185265,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T07:16:50.000Z","msg":"歐盟外交及防衛事務高級代表莫姬莉妮就天安門廣場事件30週件發表聲明，表示：<br />\n1、1989年6月歐盟馬德里峰會的聲明譴責中國鎮壓民運，歐盟至今仍向死難者哀悼，向死難者家屬致哀；<br />\n2、承認當時曾發生的事對後代十分重要，認為跟該事件有關的人士應獲法律保障，並尊重紀念此事的活動；<br />\n3、敦促中國立即釋放維權人士；<br />\n4、聯合國反酷刑委員會2016年曾就天安門學運發出建議，歐盟希望中國全面落實這些建議<br />\n5、歐盟會持續跟中國就人權議題進行對話<br />\n<br />\nSource: 歐洲動態 FB<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nStatement by High Representative/Vice-President Mogherini on the 30th Anniversary of Tiananmen Square event<br />\n<a href=\"https://eeas.europa.eu/headquarters/headquarters-homepage/63615/statement-high-representativevice-president-mogherini-30th-anniversary-tiananmen-square-event_en?fbclid=IwAR183rSv5UT4AoIyG-F8l33lowL3h2YJDwfUAEXbKyOgqXK-H3kx9uRCGRI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Feeas.europa.eu%2Fheadquarters%2Fheadquarters-homepage%2F63615%2Fstatement-high-representativevice-president-mogherini-30th-anniversary-tiananmen-square-event_en%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR183rSv5UT4AoIyG-F8l33lowL3h2YJDwfUAEXbKyOgqXK-H3kx9uRCGRI&d=nhC78NoCA6QB0w8lKR9CgsrrJHX4TENqAnNRziDaZDA%3D&h=dafb86af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://eeas.europa.eu/headquarters/headquarters-homepage/63615/statement-high-representativevice-president-mogherini-30th-anniversary-tiananmen-square-event_en?fbclid=IwAR183rSv5UT4AoIyG-F8l33lowL3h2YJDwfUAEXbKyOgqXK-H3kx9uRCGRI</a>"},{"pid":"f283a0c832703d6b9a658099916f4f2d11f0cf7b","tid":1185265,"uid":28641,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T07:17:38.000Z","msg":"比完掌聲自己之後<br />\n諗下69點加大啦<br />\n支那港畜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82321aaa7d4b6ba8a1e8b28d1dc71c6ec5e33fe0","tid":1185265,"uid":76776,"lik